data.description: Mobile home one a fixed foundation in a quiet part of Dalzell. Home has a nice sized front and side porches, large living room with a fireplace, sun room, laundry room with a washer and dryer, nice kitchen with butcher block counters. The primary bedroom is very large and has an impressive bathroom attached.   New photos coming soon!
